{"title":"清晨的阳光不算温暖","authors":["郝苏民"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":12,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"清晨的阳光不算温暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（蒙古谚语）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清晨的阳光不算温暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞬息的安逸不算幸福。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作着的傻子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比睡在床上的聪明人强；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能周游四方的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比坐烂褥子的能干人强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤恳的人只讲实干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懒惰的人贪馋茶饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郝苏民选译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}